(6,71,'Siamese','The Siamese cat is a sleek, short-haired breed known for its striking blue eyes, color-point coat, and highly social personality. They are intelligent, vocal, and form strong bonds with their owners. Siamese cats are active, playful, and enjoy constant interaction. They do not like being left alone for long periods and thrive in homes where they receive attention, stimulation, and companionship.','Affectionate, Vocal, Intelligent, Social, Energetic','uploads/breeds/siamese.png','High','High','Low','Medium','Easy','Medium','Loud','High','Medium','High','High','Beginner','Simple','Medium','Medium',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','High','3,000–8,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–20 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 20:53:32',NULL),
(7,71,'Himalayan','The Himalayan cat is a long-haired breed created by crossing Persian and Siamese cats. It has a fluffy coat, flat face, and striking blue eyes with color-point markings. Himalayans are calm, affectionate, and enjoy quiet indoor living. They are people-oriented but less active, preferring relaxed companionship over high energy play. They require regular grooming due to their long coat.','Calm, Gentle, Affectionate, Quiet, Friendly','uploads/breeds/himalayan.png','Low','Low','High','Medium','Moderate','High','Low','Medium','Low','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','High','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–12,000 PHP/month (approx.)','9–15 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 20:55:18',NULL),
(8,71,'Russian Blue','The Russian Blue is a short-haired cat breed known for its elegant silver-blue coat and bright green eyes. It is intelligent, quiet, and very loyal to its owners. Russian Blues are gentle and slightly reserved with strangers but form strong bonds with their family. They are clean, low-odor cats and are generally well-behaved, making them great indoor pets.','Gentle, Quiet, Intelligent, Loyal, Shy with Strangers','uploads/breeds/russian_blue.png','Medium','Medium','Low','Medium','Easy','Medium','Low','Medium','Medium','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','High','Medium',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','High','3,000–7,000 PHP/month (approx.)','15–20 years',1,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 20:56:34',NULL),
(9,71,'Bengal','The Bengal cat is an active, athletic breed known for its wild leopard-like appearance with spotted or marbled coats. It is highly intelligent, energetic, and curious. Bengals love climbing, exploring, and playing, often requiring lots of stimulation and space. They are social cats but can be demanding due to their high activity level and strong hunting instincts.','Energetic, Intelligent, Curious, Playful, Bold','uploads/breeds/bengal.png','High','High','Low','Large','Moderate','Medium','Moderate','High','High','High','High','Intermediate','Moderate','Medium','Medium',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–15,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–16 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 20:58:02',NULL),
(10,71,'British Shorthair','The British Shorthair is a sturdy, medium-to-large cat breed known for its round face, dense plush coat, and calm personality. It is independent but affectionate, enjoying companionship without being overly demanding. This breed is low-energy, easygoing, and well-suited for indoor living. It is one of the most adaptable and low-maintenance cat breeds.','Calm, Independent, Loyal, Gentle, Easygoing','uploads/breeds/british_shorthair.png','Low','Medium','Medium','Medium','Easy','Medium','Low','Medium','Medium','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','High','Medium',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','High','3,000–8,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–20 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 20:59:33',NULL),
(11,71,'Maine Coon','The Maine Coon is one of the largest domestic cat breeds, known for its long fluffy coat, tufted ears, and friendly “gentle giant” personality. Despite its size, it is affectionate, intelligent, and highly sociable. Maine Coons are playful and enjoy interaction but are not overly demanding. They adapt well to families and are known for their friendly, dog-like behavior.','Friendly, Gentle, Social, Intelligent, Playful','uploads/breeds/maine_coon.png','Medium','Medium','High','Large','Easy','Medium','Moderate','High','Medium','High','Medium','Beginner','Moderate','High','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–12,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–15 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:00:53',NULL),
(12,71,'Persian Cat','The Persian cat is a long-haired breed known for its flat face, round eyes, and luxurious coat. It is calm, quiet, and highly affectionate with its owners. Persians prefer a peaceful indoor lifestyle and enjoy relaxing in comfortable environments. They are gentle companions but require regular grooming due to their thick fur.','Calm, Gentle, Affectionate, Quiet, Relaxed','uploads/breeds/persian.png','Low','Low','High','Medium','Easy','High','Low','Medium','Low','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','High','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–15,000 PHP/month (approx.)','10–15 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:02:04',NULL),
(13,71,'Puspin (Pusang Pinoy / Domestic Short-Haired Cat)','The Puspin is the common domestic cat found in the Philippines. They are not a formal breed but a mixed population of local short-haired cats. Puspins are adaptable, intelligent, and resilient, often thriving in various environments. They can be affectionate, playful, and independent depending on upbringing. They are low-maintenance pets and are well-suited for first-time cat owners.','Adaptable, Independent, Friendly, Intelligent, Resilient','uploads/breeds/puspin.png','Medium','Medium','Low','Medium','Easy','Medium','Moderate','Medium','Medium','Medium','Low','Beginner','Simple','Medium','Medium',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','Medium','1,000–4,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–18 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:03:24',NULL),
(14,71,'Ragdoll','The Ragdoll is a large, affectionate cat breed known for its striking blue eyes, semi-long silky coat, and very relaxed temperament. They are famously gentle and often go limp when held, which is how they got their name. Ragdolls are highly social, loving, and enjoy being around people, making them ideal companion pets for calm households.','Gentle, Affectionate, Calm, Social, Easygoing','uploads/breeds/ragdoll.png','Medium','Medium','High','Medium','Easy','High','Low','High','Medium','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','High','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–12,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–17 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:04:36',NULL),
(15,70,'American Bully','The American Bully is a muscular, medium-to-large dog breed known for its strong build, confident appearance, and affectionate nature. Despite its intimidating look, it is generally gentle, loyal, and people-oriented. American Bullies are social dogs that enjoy family life and thrive on companionship, training, and structure. They require responsible ownership, early socialization, and consistent exercise.','Loyal, Confident, Affectionate, Friendly, Protective','uploads/breeds/american_bully.png','Medium','High','Low','Large','Moderate','Medium','Moderate','High','None','High','High','Intermediate','Moderate','Low','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–15,000 PHP/month (approx.)','10–13 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:09:29',NULL),
(16,70,'Aspin (Asong Pinoy / Philippine Native Dog)','The Aspin is the common mixed-breed dog found in the Philippines. They are known for their resilience, adaptability, and strong survival instincts. Aspins vary widely in size, appearance, and temperament, but many are loyal, intelligent, and affectionate when properly cared for. They are low-maintenance dogs that adapt well to different environments, making them excellent family companions and rescue pets.','Loyal, Intelligent, Adaptable, Protective, Friendly','uploads/breeds/aspin.png','Medium','Medium','Low','Medium','Moderate','Medium','Moderate','Medium','None','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','Medium','Medium',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','Medium','1,500–5,000 PHP/month (approx.)','10–15 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:11:36',NULL),
(17,70,'Beagle','The Beagle is a small-to-medium hunting dog breed known for its strong sense of smell, energetic personality, and friendly nature. Originally bred for tracking and hunting, Beagles are curious, active, and love to explore. They are social dogs that enjoy being around people and other dogs, making them great family pets when properly trained and exercised.','Friendly, Curious, Energetic, Playful, Sociable','uploads/breeds/beagle.png','High','High','Low','Large','Moderate','Medium','Loud','High','None','High','High','Intermediate','Moderate','High','Medium',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','High','3,000–10,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–15 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:12:58',NULL),
(18,70,'Chihuahua','The Chihuahua is one of the smallest dog breeds in the world, known for its big personality despite its tiny size. It is loyal, alert, and often forms a strong bond with its owner. Chihuahuas can be confident, vocal, and sometimes protective. They adapt well to small living spaces and are popular companion dogs.','Loyal, Alert, Confident, Vocal, Affectionate','uploads/breeds/chihuahua.png','Medium','Medium','Low','Small','Moderate','High','Loud','High','None','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','Medium','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','High','2,000–8,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–20 years',0,0,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:14:24',NULL),
(19,70,'Chow Chow','The Chow Chow is a medium-to-large dog breed known for its lion-like appearance, thick fluffy coat, and unique blue-black tongue. It is an independent, reserved, and dignified breed that is often loyal to one or a few people. Chow Chows are calm but can be strong-willed and require early training and socialization. They prefer a quiet, structured environment.','Independent, Loyal, Reserved, Calm, Strong-willed','uploads/breeds/chow_chow.png','Medium','Medium','High','Large','Difficult','Low','Low','Medium','None','High','Medium','Advanced','Complex','Medium','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–15,000 PHP/month (approx.)','9–15 years',0,0,0,0,0,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:15:46',NULL),
(20,70,'Pembroke Welsh Corgi','The Corgi is a small-to-medium herding dog breed known for its short legs, long body, and friendly personality. Originally bred for herding cattle, Corgis are intelligent, active, and alert. They are affectionate family dogs that enjoy companionship and mental stimulation. Despite their size, they are energetic and need regular exercise.','Friendly, Intelligent, Energetic, Playful, Alert','uploads/breeds/corgi_pembroke_welsh.png','High','High','Medium','Medium','Moderate','Medium','Loud','High','None','High','High','Beginner','Moderate','High','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','3,000–10,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–15 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:17:16',NULL),
(21,70,'Dachshund','The Dachshund is a small, long-bodied dog breed originally bred for hunting burrow-dwelling animals. It is curious, brave, and sometimes stubborn. Dachshunds are affectionate with their owners and can be playful and entertaining. They come in smooth, long-haired, and wire-haired coat types and adapt well to home living.','Brave, Curious, Loyal, Playful, Stubborn','uploads/breeds/dachshund.png','Medium','Medium','Medium','Medium','Difficult','Medium','Loud','High','None','Medium','Medium','Intermediate','Simple','Medium','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','High','3,000–10,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–16 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:18:47',NULL),
(22,70,'French Bulldog','The French Bulldog is a small, sturdy companion dog known for its bat-like ears, short snout, and affectionate personality. It is playful, social, and loves being close to its owner. French Bulldogs adapt well to apartment living and do not require heavy exercise, making them popular companion pets. However, they need careful health monitoring due to breathing sensitivity.','Affectionate, Playful, Friendly, Calm, Social','uploads/breeds/french_bulldog.png','Medium','Medium','Low','Small','Moderate','High','Moderate','High','None','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','High','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–15,000 PHP/month (approx.)','10–12 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:19:56',NULL),
(23,70,'German Shepherd','The German Shepherd is a large, intelligent, and versatile working dog breed known for its loyalty, strength, and trainability. Originally developed for herding and protection work, it is widely used in police, military, and service roles. German Shepherds are highly loyal, protective, and require consistent training, exercise, and mental stimulation. They thrive in active households with strong leadership.','Loyal, Intelligent, Protective, Confident, Obedient','uploads/breeds/german_shepherd.png','High','High','High','Large','Moderate','Medium','Loud','High','None','High','High','Advanced','Moderate','Medium','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–15,000 PHP/month (approx.)','9–13 years',0,1,0,1,1,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:21:15',NULL),
(24,70,'Golden Retriever','The Golden Retriever is a large, friendly, and intelligent dog breed known for its golden coat and gentle nature. It is one of the most popular family dogs due to its affectionate, patient, and social personality. Golden Retrievers are highly trainable and often used as service and therapy dogs. They thrive in active households with regular exercise and companionship.','Friendly, Gentle, Intelligent, Loyal, Social','uploads/breeds/golden_retriever.png','High','High','High','Large','Easy','High','Moderate','High','None','High','High','Beginner','Moderate','High','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–15,000 PHP/month (approx.)','10–12 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:22:21',NULL),
(25,70,'Japanese Spitz','The Japanese Spitz is a small-to-medium companion dog known for its fluffy white coat, fox-like face, and friendly personality. It is cheerful, loyal, and highly affectionate with families. This breed is intelligent, easy to train, and enjoys being around people. Japanese Spitz dogs are active but adaptable, making them well-suited for both houses and apartments.','Friendly, Loyal, Playful, Intelligent, Social','uploads/breeds/japanese_spitz.png','Medium','Medium','High','Medium','Easy','High','Loud','High','None','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','High','Medium',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','High','3,000–10,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–16 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:23:21',NULL),
(26,70,'Labrador Retriever','The Labrador Retriever is a large, friendly, and highly intelligent dog breed known for its loyal and outgoing nature. It is one of the most popular family dogs worldwide due to its gentle temperament and strong trainability. Labradors are active, social, and love to play, especially in water. They are often used as service, therapy, and working dogs because of their reliability and obedience.','Friendly, Gentle, Intelligent, Outgoing, Loyal','uploads/breeds/labrador_retriever.png','High','High','Medium','Large','Easy','High','Moderate','High','None','High','High','Beginner','Moderate','High','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–15,000 PHP/month (approx.)','10–14 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:24:39',NULL),
(27,70,'Pomeranian','The Pomeranian is a small, fluffy companion dog known for its fox-like face, thick double coat, and lively personality. Despite its tiny size, it is bold, alert, and confident. Pomeranians are affectionate and enjoy attention, often forming strong bonds with their owners. They are active indoors and adapt well to apartment living, but require regular grooming and social interaction.','Lively, Confident, Affectionate, Alert, Playful','uploads/breeds/pomeranian.png','Medium','Medium','High','Small','Moderate','High','Loud','High','None','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','Medium','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','High','3,000–10,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–16 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:25:46',NULL),
(28,70,'Shih Tzu','The Shih Tzu is a small companion dog known for its long, flowing coat and friendly, affectionate personality. Originally bred as a royal lap dog, it enjoys close human companionship and prefers indoor living. Shih Tzus are gentle, playful, and adaptable, making them popular family pets. They require regular grooming to maintain their coat and overall hygiene.','Friendly, Affectionate, Gentle, Playful, Outgoing','uploads/breeds/shihtzu.png','Medium','Medium','High','Small','Moderate','High','Moderate','High','None','Medium','Medium','Beginner','Simple','High','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','Medium','High','3,000–10,000 PHP/month (approx.)','10–16 years',0,1,0,1,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:26:49',NULL),
(29,70,'Siberian Husky','The Siberian Husky is a medium-to-large working dog breed originally bred for sled pulling in cold climates. It is known for its striking appearance, thick double coat, and energetic, independent personality. Huskies are intelligent, social, and playful but can be stubborn and strong-willed. They require active owners who can provide plenty of exercise and mental stimulation.','Energetic, Independent, Friendly, Intelligent, Playful','uploads/breeds/siberian_husky.png','High','High','High','Large','Difficult','Medium','Loud','High','None','High','High','Advanced','Complex','Medium','High',NULL,'Low','Medium','High','High','5,000–15,000 PHP/month (approx.)','12–15 years',0,1,0,1,0,0,NULL,0,1,NULL,'2026-04-25 21:27:58',NULL),
